title: Valiance Line
summary: The Valiance Line focuses on speed and regeneration. Because of their light health pool, they tend to not be used by more experienced players, but they are popular among newer players because of their cheaper manufacturing costs. With speed and regeneration, they are naturally used as dedicated sniper ships.
full_text:
Valiance Line
The Valiance Line focuses on speed and regeneration. Because of their light health pool, they tend to not be used by more experienced players, but they are popular among newer players because of their cheaper manufacturing costs. With speed and regeneration, they are naturally used as dedicated sniper ships.
